videos.description: Andrew Eudy throws down a nice two-handed jam off a back cut to cut into Winthrop's lead.
videos.headline: Eudy throws it down off the back cut for Campbell

videos.description: Keon Johnson opens the second half with back-to-back 3-point shots after being held to six points in the first half.
videos.headline: Winthrop's Johnson finding shot early in 2nd half

videos.description: Chris Clemons finishes a tough layup over a taller defender.
videos.headline: Campbell's Clemons makes great layup

videos.description: Keon Johnson splits two defenders to put away a wide open layup.
videos.headline: Winthrop's Johnson splits defenders to finish at the basket

videos.description: Winthrop fans are dancing again after winning the Big South Tournament for the first time since 2010.
videos.headline: Winthrop fans storm the court after winning the Big South Tournament

videos.description: Winthrop players and fans celebrate making their first tournament appearance since 2010, after winning the Big South Conference Tournament
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown on Winthrop's first tournament appearance since 2010
